  <div class="hero-text" data-aos="fade-right">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">
      Discover Your Next Stay <br>
      <span class="gradient-text">with Wanderlite</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">
      Find beautiful stays around the world — from peaceful mountain cabins to cozy city apartments.
